705949f-a.title: Brooklyn: Nevins Street - Livingston Street
705949f-a.text:
Nevins Street, west side, south from Livingston Street. The large
building in the center background, is the Harriet Judson Y.W.C.A.
April 24, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
